Summary:      Library for manipulating RDF files describing LADSPA plugins
Summary(zh_CN.UTF-8): 处理描述 LADSPA 插件的 RDF 文件的库
Name:         liblrdf
Version:      0.5.0
Release:      5%{?dist}
License:      GPLv2+
Group:        System Environment/Libraries
Group(zh_CN.UTF-8): 系统环境/库
URL:          https://github.com/swh/LRDF
